snippet.title: SUPER LAURA UP - RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
I'm a an indie dev with my friends. This game is a mix of getting over it with benet fodd, only up, mario, jump king and so many more. Check it out over here: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2684010/Super_Laura_Up/

I hope you like it! and sorry for the falls O.O
